# systemd + Python venv 服务模板

## 标准模板（系统Python）
```ini
[Unit]
Description=My Service
After=network.target

[Service]
Type=simple
User=admin
WorkingDirectory=/opt/project
ExecStart=/usr/bin/python3 /opt/project/app.py
Restart=always
RestartSec=5
EnvironmentFile=-/opt/project/.env

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
```

## venv Python 模板（推荐）
```ini
[Unit]
Description=My Service
After=network.target

[Service]
Type=simple
User=admin
WorkingDirectory=/opt/project
ExecStart=/home/admin/.hermes/hermes-agent/venv/bin/python3 /opt/project/app.py
Restart=always
RestartSec=5
Environment=PORT=8080
Environment=ADMIN_TOKEN=secret123

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
```

## 调试命令
```bash
systemctl status service-name --no-pager
journalctl -u service-name -n 30 --no-pager
systemctl daemon-reload && systemctl restart service-name
```
